  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your problem solving skills and creativity in over 80 physics-based puzzles. Help guide the red ball to the exit by placing movable objects before turning gravity on.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208960/extras/dccf3d32800e34bf541c60aa2c5db3de.poster.avif?t=1761593069\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208960/extras/dccf3d32800e34bf541c60aa2c5db3de.webm?t=1761593069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208960/extras/dccf3d32800e34bf541c60aa2c5db3de.mp4?t=1761593069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Yellow</strong> – movable, affected by gravity             <strong>Orange</strong> – movable, not affected by gravity</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pink</strong> – movable, affected by anti-gravity         <strong>Green</strong> – static, affected by gravity</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208960/extras/2f8da367504ada187cf7f5d0a5d6fab4.poster.avif?t=1761593069\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208960/extras/2f8da367504ada187cf7f5d0a5d6fab4.webm?t=1761593069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208960/extras/2f8da367504ada187cf7f5d0a5d6fab4.mp4?t=1761593069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let Your creativity shine with multiple ways to complete every level!</p>",
